{"tid":39993,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"金融行業 IT support 做左十年, 你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-15T02:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T07:30:24.000Z","uid":65704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19604cd7b2bebc29bb4cb5917c8eead91d4252b5","tid":39993,"uid":65704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:05:05.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人有興趣，主力做 infra"},{"pid":"54e365043f96aa901e1bcfd9876437b10242d55b","tid":39993,"uid":48012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:06:21.000Z","msg":"Operations<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7acd18aba5917c6afce728dd45cbfff134df3b","tid":39993,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:08:44.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"b523914b39c886af6f3c6b10d0c1801fc1573e2c","tid":39993,"uid":65704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Operations<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBuy side 定  sell side <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac1c5a9d22c7b3a961d00719f71c2ee6b440765","tid":39993,"uid":2176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:29:57.000Z","msg":"人工好唔好? 我都做緊infra"},{"pid":"90daaea031ef2d62bafd05437dc1cbd20cc210bb","tid":39993,"uid":65704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人工好唔好? 我都做緊infra</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇運，正常有五六年呢行經驗要搵 40k 以上唔難，有 d 人做 infra support 都過百萬一年，（連b 仔）"},{"pid":"25ecd447d644cbab812e019a67c52ea4d64470c4","tid":39993,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"要support咩system?係咪好舊？"},{"pid":"4f34395ecc98f163f8fd71ccdc55478b450f305c","tid":39993,"uid":65704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要support咩system?係咪好舊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黎黎去去最多咪係 M$ 野， 跟住有 d 會係 unix/Linux , 近呢十年都叫新野多過舊野， 如果 user 個邊九城都係 M$"},{"pid":"ea991d02b5435008a1873c8248e06b4de9afcb1f","tid":39993,"uid":31689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:51:40.000Z","msg":"Hardware support 定software support?<br />\n其實主要係做啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果係某大型it mnc做緊onsite support 有冇咩方法轉行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4fafe11584f0876fdbf2eda29595e5d4aed22a","tid":39993,"uid":65704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hardware support 定software support?<br />\n其實主要係做啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果係某大型it mnc做緊onsite support 有冇咩方法轉行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做 infra 既多數都係睇  server 同 os, 跟住就 network, telecom (電話）等等都有， 當然有時都要做埋 user side support, 主要睇你間公司同條 team 有幾多人，做 bank 既話人多但功能分得好細， 做細公司既人工未必會少得過銀行，<br />\n<br />\n巴打做開 mnc, 英文 talk 得既話唔難入"},{"pid":"b1409dd2bdb50b9052023b884e7a4ed5ad7361bf","tid":39993,"uid":2026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:06:04.000Z","msg":"做緊 SI infra. 主力做unix Linix. 最近有掂下 telcom project 做下tester. 不過我個degree 唔係it related. <br />\n<br />\n如果想轉做Inhouse support/engineer，要唔要考返個it master 好d. <br />\n<br />\n另外想問做落去應該點去提升返自己？<br />\n<br />\nSI 公司係咪最好做幾年就走？"},{"pid":"b4e9dd45aec211488511523685f80bcc442a8b10","tid":39993,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Operations<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBuy side 定  sell side <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定係buy sell架咩<br />\nremittance唔得？"},{"pid":"8c416a5f773e9b48b89f51f669d624849e4199cb","tid":39993,"uid":62079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知有冇人有興趣，主力做 infra</blockquote><br />\ndegree讀乜入行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ec5cfa7a0a996975e30a858084c142a23f0ce4","tid":39993,"uid":65704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Operations<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBuy side 定  sell side <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定係buy sell架咩<br />\nremittance唔得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留名學野， remittance 做乜多"},{"pid":"40d54a106a0c34b1ff0a9809ef2aab64c1a663f6","tid":39993,"uid":65704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做緊 SI infra. 主力做unix Linix. 最近有掂下 telcom project 做下tester. 不過我個degree 唔係it related. <br />\n<br />\n如果想轉做Inhouse support/engineer，要唔要考返個it master 好d. <br />\n<br />\n另外想問做落去應該點去提升返自己？<br />\n<br />\nSI 公司係咪最好做幾年就走？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識人好過識字，我本身都冇 degree, 一樣可以升到  VP, SI 有野學不過辛苦就一定， inhouse 其實可以好悶，日日返去睇 forum (前題 d 野要 set 得好好囉），最最緊要係練好英文，無往而不利"},{"pid":"2e048823ed418e683924ab59a802cc5eafeabe00","tid":39993,"uid":65704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知有冇人有興趣，主力做 infra</blockquote><br />\ndegree讀乜入行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中學畢業"}]}